                                <height>0.54</height><depth atLeast="0.155" atMost="0.17">0.155-0.17</depth></dimensions>), beginning at <dim type="distance">0.09</dim> 
                                    under the moulding; both lines were aligned following the left edge.</layout> 
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
